title: Blow Skirt
description:
Download the Funny application "Skirt Blow" on your android mobile phones for free and have fun. 
Game is very simple and fun, as long as you blow into the microphone will simulate the strength of the wind, skirt blowing will vary depending on your strength of different degrees of swing, so you can see beautiful scenery under the skirt.
Blow over the Sweet Lady's skirt in the given time period and watch her skirt rise. The harder you blow, the higher skirt.image
- xmaaza
